title: Palms
typeOfFood: Lacto, Ovo, American, Western, Salad bar, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Hyatt hotel restaurant, shares a kitchen with the other restaurants there but has a separate kitchen for gluten-free. Menu is mostly meat stuff but does have a veggie burger and gluten free bread which are both vegan suitable. Dinner menu has a veggie wrap that's vegan.
